# =============================================================================
# Dataset - Ignore large training data, KEEP source code in data/ folders
# =============================================================================
# KHÔNG dùng **/data/ vì sẽ chặn source code (vd: DRCT/drct/data/)
# Chỉ ignore dataset contents cụ thể
**/datasets/**/*.png
**/datasets/**/*.jpg
**/datasets/**/*.jpeg
**/datasets/**/*.bmp
**/datasets/**/*.tiff
**/datasets/**/*.npy
**/datasets/**/*.lmdb
**/datasets/**/*.mdb

# =============================================================================
# Images - Ignore output/generated images, KEEP test data & assets nhỏ
# =============================================================================
# Ignore ảnh trong Visualization output
**/Visualization/**/*.png
**/Visualization/**/*.jpg

# =============================================================================
# Agent Context / Prompt Markdown Files
# =============================================================================
